'''Badoo'''上是一个以约会为中心的[[社交网络服务|社交网络服务]]，<ref name="techcrunch.com">{{cite web|url=http://techcrunch.com/2012/05/04/badabing-badaboom-badoo-hits-150-million-users-boosted-by-mobile/|title=Badabing Badaboom – Badoo Hits 150 Million Users, Boosted By Mobile|work=TechCrunch|publisher=AOL|accessdate=2016-10-02|archive-date=2015-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117025502/http://techcrunch.com/2012/05/04/badabing-badaboom-badoo-hits-150-million-users-boosted-by-mobile/|dead-url=no}}</ref>成立于2006年，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://eu.techcrunch.com/2012/01/19/hey-tagged-badoo-has-been-around-as-long-and-has-bigger-revenues/|title=Hey Tagged, Badoo Has Been Around As Long And Has Bigger Revenues|work=TechCrunch|publisher=AOL|accessdate=2016-10-02|archive-date=2012-02-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120221122456/http://eu.techcrunch.com/2012/01/19/hey-tagged-badoo-has-been-around-as-long-and-has-bigger-revenues/|dead-url=no}}</ref>总部位于[[伦敦|伦敦]][[苏荷区|苏荷区]]。Badoo向180多个国家服务，<ref>{{cite news|url=http://blogs.wsj.com/tech-europe/2012/01/24/the-very-social-network/?mod=google_news_blog|title=A Very Social Network|last=Rooney|first=Ben|date=2012-01-24|work=The Wall Street Journal|accessdate=2016-10-02|archive-date=2015-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117020559/http://blogs.wsj.com/tech-europe/2012/01/24/the-very-social-network/?mod=google_news_blog|dead-url=no}}</ref>在拉丁美洲、西班牙、意大利和法国最为流行，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://trends.google.com/websites?q=badoo.com|title=Google.com|accessdate=2010-08-31|archive-date=2011-08-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110831114439/http://trends.google.com/websites?q=badoo.com|dead-url=no}}</ref>其运营模式为[[免费增值|免费增值模式]]。2014年4月，Badoo被[[Alexa_Internet|Alexa]]列为世界上第281大最受欢迎的网站之一。为了获取额外功能，用户可以付费或允许Badoo向用户的朋友发送电子邮件。

== 历史 ==
2006年11月，俄罗斯企业家安德烈·安德烈耶夫创立了Badoo，总部位于英国伦敦。<ref name="Finam">{{cite web |url=http://www.finamcapital.com/badoo.html |title=Project Portfolio – Badoo |accessdate=2011-02-10 |year=2009 |publisher=Finam Capital |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110228005937/http://www.finamcapital.com/badoo.html |archivedate=2011-02-28 }}</ref>到了2007年，Badoo共募集了3000万美元。<ref name="cnet">{{cite news|url=http://www.cnet.com/news/badoo-social-experiment-or-hookup-site/|title=Badoo: Social experiment or hookup site?|last=Needleman|first=Rafe|date=February 23, 2012|publisher=CNET|accessdate=May 29, 2014|archive-date=2016-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160809072316/http://www.cnet.com/news/badoo-social-experiment-or-hookup-site/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2008年1月，俄罗斯投资者Finam Capital以3000万美元的价格购买了Badoo10％的股权，并希望以此将市场扩张至俄罗斯。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://uk.techcrunch.com/2008/01/21/uks-badoo-pulls-30m-for-russian-launch-ahead-of-a-home-push/|title=UK’s Badoo pulls $30m for Russian launch, ahead of a home push|accessdate=2009-08-29|date=21 January 2008|last=Butcher|first=Mike|publisher=Techcrunch|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090812150108/http://uk.techcrunch.com/2008/01/21/uks-badoo-pulls-30m-for-russian-launch-ahead-of-a-home-push/|archive-date=2009-08-12|dead-url=yes}}</ref>截至2009年，Finam Capital控制人Badoo20％的股权。<ref name="Finam2">{{cite web |url=http://www.finamcapital.com/badoo.html |title=Project Portfolio – Badoo |accessdate=2011-02-10 |year=2009 |publisher=Finam Capital |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110228005937/http://www.finamcapital.com/badoo.html |archivedate=2011-02-28 }}</ref>

2011年4月，Badoo受到了Facebook的威胁，如果其Facebook客户端的病毒数量没有减少，Badoo可能被移除。<ref>[http://www.businessinsider.com/badoo-facebook-2011-4 www.businessinsider.com/badoo-facebook-2011-4] {{Wayback|url=http://www.businessinsider.com/badoo-facebook-2011-4 |date=20161003055359 }}.</ref>根据Insidefacebook.com的消息，在1月11日当周，Badoo的Facebook客户端增长率名列第17位。2012年3月23日，Badoo官方进军美国市场，[[尼克·卡农|尼克·卡农]]在美国全力介绍其服务。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mashable.com/2012/03/23/badoo-us/#55251Badoo-Project-in-New-York-City|title=Social Network Badoo Officially Launches in U.S. With Nick Cannon [PICS]|date=23 March 2012|work=Mashable|accessdate=2016-10-02|archive-date=2016-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161003063018/http://mashable.com/2012/03/23/badoo-us/#55251Badoo-Project-in-New-York-City|dead-url=no}}</ref>2012年4月，Badoo与Hot or Not达成了一封营销协议以在其公司服务显示其成员。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://techcrunch.com/2012/04/02/has-dating-site-badoo-found-a-love-match-in-the-form-of-hotornot/|title=Updated: Has Dating Site Badoo Found A Love Match In The Form Of Hot or Not?|work=TechCrunch|publisher=AOL|accessdate=2016-10-02|archive-date=2016-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160925223913/https://techcrunch.com/2012/04/02/has-dating-site-badoo-found-a-love-match-in-the-form-of-hotornot/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2016年2月，Badoo收购了一款让女性匿名给男性评价打分的移动应用程序[[LuLu_(应用程序)|LuLu]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://techcrunch.com/2016/02/09/lulu-marries-badoo/|title=Lulu, The App That Lets Women Rate Men, Acquired By Badoo|accessdate=February 9, 2016|date=February 9, 2016|work=TechCrunch|archive-date=2016-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160924110521/https://techcrunch.com/2016/02/09/lulu-marries-badoo/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 特性 ==
<!-- 因文件已删，故注解：[[File:Badoo_的截图.png|左]] -->
Badoo是一个免费增值服务，其基本服务是完全免费的，但也有一些高级功能需付费才可使用。使用者注册后，他们就可以聊天、上传影像。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.businessinsider.com/badoo-2011-2#if-you-want-to-chat-with-someone-you-need-to-register-for-an-account-3|title=The Biggest Startup You've Never Heard Of Is About To Hit 108 Million Members|accessdate=31 October 2013|last=Frommer|first=Dan|publisher=Business Insider|archive-date=2016-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160805142236/http://www.businessinsider.com/badoo-2011-2#if-you-want-to-chat-with-someone-you-need-to-register-for-an-account-3|dead-url=no}}</ref>使用者还可以通过“附近会员”在用户所在地或“搜索”在世界上的其他地区发现其他使用者并同他们取得联系。<ref name="Fromer2">{{cite web|url=http://www.businessinsider.com/badoo-2011-2#this-is-what-badoos-iphone-app-looks-like-when-you-first-launch-it-just-one-of-many-ways-to-use-the-service-smartly-you-can-do-things-without-registering-lets-look-at-people-nearby-1|title=The Biggest Startup You've Never Heard Of Is About To Hit 108 Million Members|last=Fromer|first=Dan|publisher=Business Insider|accessdate=2016-10-03|archive-date=2016-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160805142236/http://www.businessinsider.com/badoo-2011-2#this-is-what-badoos-iphone-app-looks-like-when-you-first-launch-it-just-one-of-many-ways-to-use-the-service-smartly-you-can-do-things-without-registering-lets-look-at-people-nearby-1|dead-url=no}}</ref>另一个免费的功能是“邂逅游戏”，在游戏中，用户需要点击“是”或“否”以判断照片上的人是否为某用户，如果回答正确，两个用户都会收到通知。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.businessinsider.com/badoo-2011-2#once-weve-signed-up-for-an-account-theres-a-bunch-of-new-stuff-we-can-do-one-fun-feature-is-encounters-a-sort-of-hot-or-not-game-4|title=The Biggest Startup You've Never Heard Of Is About To Hit 108 Million Members|last=Frommer|first=Dan|accessdate=2016-10-03|archive-date=2016-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160805142236/http://www.businessinsider.com/badoo-2011-2#once-weve-signed-up-for-an-account-theres-a-bunch-of-new-stuff-we-can-do-one-fun-feature-is-encounters-a-sort-of-hot-or-not-game-4|dead-url=no}}</ref>如付费，用户就可以使用“上升”。在一定时间内，它会让用户的个人资料在网站上的拥有更高的知名度。Badoo的通信主管乔治·露西表示截止2007年年底，Badoo的2200万用户中20%的用户每月会为此付费至少一次以提高知名度。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://blogs.guardian.co.uk/digitalcontent/2008/03/elevator_pitch_why_badoo_wants.html|title=Elevator Pitch: Why Badoo wants to be the next word in social networking|date=24 December 2007|newspaper=The Guardian|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080308175435/http://blogs.guardian.co.uk/digitalcontent/2008/03/elevator_pitch_why_badoo_wants.html|archivedate=2008-03-08|author=Sweney, Mark|accessdate=2016-10-03}}</ref>但是根据[[经济学人|经济学人]]的数据，截止2011年，只有5％的成员会为高级服务付费。<ref name="Economist-2011">{{Cite news|url=http://www.economist.com/blogs/babbage/2011/09/social-networking|title=A nightclub on your smartphone|date=19 September 2011|newspaper=The Economist|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110921014702/http://www.economist.com/blogs/babbage/2011/09/social-networking|archivedate=2011-09-21|accessdate=2016-10-03}}</ref>

“上升”会让用户在搜索结果中的排行更高，因此可以吸引更多人关注。用户如付费后还可以让他们个人资料中的照片在Badoo更广泛的传播。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wired.co.uk/magazine/archive/2011/05/features/sexual-network/viewall|title=How Badoo built a billion-pound social network... on sex|accessdate=31 October 2013|last=Rowan|first=David|publisher=Wired|archive-date=2016-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160314000824/http://www.wired.co.uk/magazine/archive/2011/05/features/sexual-network/viewall|dead-url=no}}</ref>购买“超级权力”后则可看到更多搜索结果、想同用户见面的人和用户发送的信息被阅读的情况。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://affiliatecolony.com/badoo-social-networking/ |title=Badoo Social Networking |accessdate=31 October 2013 |last=Adam |publisher=Affiliate Colony |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131020154634/http://affiliatecolony.com/badoo-social-networking/ |archivedate=2013-10-20 }}</ref>

Badoo还被列为了最流行的交友网站之一。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ebizmba.com/articles/dating-websites|title=Top 15 Most Popular Dating Websites|accessdate=September 28, 2015|author=|date=September 2015|publisher=eBizMBA|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160927182356/http://www.ebizmba.com/articles/dating-websites|archivedate=2016-09-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[CNET|CNET]]认为Badoo是一个旨在“为用户介绍附近兴趣相似的人”的网站。<ref name="cnet3">{{cite news|url=http://www.cnet.com/news/badoo-social-experiment-or-hookup-site/|title=Badoo: Social experiment or hookup site?|last=Needleman|first=Rafe|date=February 23, 2012|work=|publisher=CNET|accessdate=May 29, 2014|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160809072316/http://www.cnet.com/news/badoo-social-experiment-or-hookup-site/|archivedate=2016-08-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 批评与争议 ==
2009年，剑桥大学对45个社交网站展开了同行评审。<ref>{{Citation|title=The Privacy Jungle: On the Market for Privacy in Social Networks|url=http://www.jbonneau.com/doc/BP09-WEIS-privacy_jungle.pdf|year=2009|last1=Bonneau|last2=Preibusch|first1=Joseph|first2=Sören|journal=WEIS '09: Proceedings of the Eighth Workshop on the Economics of Information Security.|accessdate=2016-10-02|archive-date=2016-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160927125658/http://www.jbonneau.com/doc/BP09-WEIS-privacy_jungle.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>在关于用户隐私的调查中，Badoo的得分最低。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/news/5878857/Social-networks-failing-users-says-study.html|title=Social networks ‘failing users’, says study|accessdate=2016-10-03|author=|date=2009-07-21|publisher=The Daily Telegraph|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150729014245/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/news/5878857/Social-networks-failing-users-says-study.html|archivedate=2015-07-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>

此外，Badoo还会向愿意透露联系人信息的用户提供额外功能。<ref name="cnet2">{{cite news|url=http://www.cnet.com/news/badoo-social-experiment-or-hookup-site/|title=Badoo: Social experiment or hookup site?|last=Needleman|first=Rafe|date=February 23, 2012|work=|publisher=CNET|accessdate=May 29, 2014|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160809072316/http://www.cnet.com/news/badoo-social-experiment-or-hookup-site/|archivedate=2016-08-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>

根据[[Google|Google]][[透明度报告|透明度报告]]，为保护用户的[[被遺忘權|被遺忘權]]，Badoo在Google搜索中被删除的[[统一资源定位符|统一资源定位符]]数量位居第四位。<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.google.com/transparencyreport/removals/europeprivacy/?hl=en|title = European privacy requests for search removals|date = 17 October 2014|accessdate = 17 October 2014|website = Transparency Report|publisher = Google|last = |first = |archive-date = 2016-09-27|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160927061554/https://www.google.com/transparencyreport/removals/europeprivacy/?hl=en|dead-url = no}}</ref>

